l\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 23, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gbv1665702793496.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gbv1665702793496.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gbv1665702793496.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gbv1665702793496\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Define Keys/Indexes Worksheet\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use this worksheet to define the primary key used to identify occurrences of the entity, and fields that should be indexed.\n </p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"gbv1665702793496__note_w3426ab1b7b1_w3427ab1b7_w3428ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> In this release, it is only\n      possible to define primary keys. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ruk1704361429324.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ruk1704361429324.html\" title=\"A key is a field or combination of fields that uniquely identifies occurrences of entities.\">Keys</a>. </div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gbv1665702793496__section_z5n_k22_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d808364e65\">Tools</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"gbv1665702793496__ul_cbk_l22_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbv1665702793496__li_d2498e1_d2499e1_d2500e1\">Resource Browser—lists the field of the current entity,\n          which you can drag and drop onto the selected key in the Key Editor. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbv1665702793496__li_d2501e1_d2502e1_d2503e1\">Key Editor—shows the entity, its keys, and the fields\n          that make up each key, as a tree. You can edit properties of the selected object here or\n          in the Properties Inspector. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbv1665702793496__li_d2504e1_d2505e1_d2506e1\">Properties Inspector—shows the properties of the object\n          selected in the Key Editor, and enables you to edit them. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gbv1665702793496__section_lmq_l22_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d808364e83\">How To </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"gbv1665702793496__ul_kzv_m22_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbv1665702793496__li_d2507e1_d2508e1_d2509e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uef1704361749454.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uef1704361749454.html\" title=\"Each modeled entity must have a primary key.\">Define the Keys of a Modeled Entity</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbv1665702793496__li_d2510e1_d2511e1_d2512e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kdb1665702780441.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kdb1665702780441.html\" title=\"You can resize the width of columns by clicking the triangle in column header, and setting the desired width.\">Resize Columns</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"gbv1665702793496__ul_nzv_m22_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbv1665702793496__li_d2513e1_d2514e1_d2515e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qle1665702773192.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qle1665702773192.html\" title=\"Use the Uniface IDE to develop an application, following the Uniface development paradigm of Model, Construct, Build, and Deploy.\">Using the Uniface IDE</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gbv1665702793496__li_d2516e1_d2517e1_d2518e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dkp1665702773261.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dkp1665702773261.html\" title=\"Although development objects can be quite different in content and purpose, the way you create, edit and delete them in the Uniface IDE is essentially the same.\">Working with Development Objects</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ruk1704361429324.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Keys</a><p>A key is a field or combination of fields that uniquely identifies occurrences of entities.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527790\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527790\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Define Keys/Indexes Worksheet Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 23, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Define Keys/Indexes Worksheet Use this worksheet to define the primary key used to identify occurrences of the entity, and fields that should be indexed. Note: In this release, it is only possible to define primary keys. For more information, see Keys . Tools Resource Browser—lists the field of the current entity, which you can drag and drop onto the selected key in the Key Editor. Key Editor—shows the entity, its keys, and the fields that make up each key, as a tree. You can edit properties of the selected object here or in the Properties Inspector. Properties Inspector—shows the properties of the object selected in the Key Editor, and enables you to edit them. How To Define the Keys of a Modeled Entity Resize Columns Using the Uniface IDE Working with Development Objects Related Links Keys A key is a field or combination of fields that uniquely identifies occurrences of entities. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}